{"id": 13, "name": "Texte de la commission sur la proposition de loi de M. Olivier Falorni relative \u00e0 la fin de vie (1100)., n\u00b0\u00a01364-A0", "url": "/dyn/17/amendements/1364/AN/13", "date": "2025-05-05", "status": "Rejet\u00e9", "proposed_by": [{"first_name": "Patrick", "last_name": "Hetzel", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Juvin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Josiane", "last_name": "Corneloup", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Fabien", "last_name": "Di Filippo", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Xavier", "last_name": "Breton", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Hubert", "last_name": "Brigand", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Olivier", "last_name": "Marleix", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Anne-Laure", "last_name": "Blin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Philippe", "last_name": "Gosselin", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Sylvie", "last_name": "Bonnet", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Pierre", "last_name": "Cordier", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}, {"first_name": "Nicolas", "last_name": "Ray", "party": "Droite R\u00e9publicaine"}], "summary": "L'euthanasie ne peut \u00eatre consid\u00e9r\u00e9e comme \"une aide \u00e0 mourir\" puisque cette proc\u00e9dure implique que le patient ne s'administre pas lui-m\u00eame la substance l\u00e9tale. En effet, s'il s'agissait d'\"une aide\", il y aurait alors une co-action. Puisque tel n'est pas le cas, il convient de supprimer la fin de l'alin\u00e9a 6 et de ne conserver que la premi\u00e8re partie qui, elle, fait r\u00e9f\u00e9rence au suicide assist\u00e9.\n"}